Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I've been a psychiatrist for 35 years, worked in the fields of psychoanalysis, nutrition, and its relationship to brain chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For the last 10 years, I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness itself and its relationship to that which the world calls spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our subject for today in today's talk is spiritual first aid, perhaps better, how to prevent the need for spiritual first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will be talking about various principles, things we've discovered through our own research,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,things that are perhaps not generally known and we feel should be of great importance to those who are involved in spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,including the idea of spiritual first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual aspects of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In this series, we've talked about the relationship between body, mind, and spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body reflects what the mind believes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind in turn reflecting that which is held in spirit, that which is held in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this series, we've talked about handling man's problems directly within the area in which they are experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is within consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In this series, we've talked about handling man's problems directly within the area in which they are experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is within consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For as we have said, the body is experienced in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no way to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind itself does not experience itself, but is experienced in a greater energy field called consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we will be looking at this directly today in talking about spiritual first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In this series, we'll be talking about how to create a safe context from which to approach one's spiritual first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll also be talking about psychological work, a concept that is not prevalent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll notice for the last ten years, I said I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,as director of the Institute for Spiritual Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual research itself is not a common thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've had to learn a great deal because much of what we'll be talking about, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,has not been written anywhere that I've run across.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of it has been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of it has been discovered.
