Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the power and the energy of their words were of such a caliber as to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to accomplish this feat even in a short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about crisis and conflict, the nature of an upset, ways of handling,
