Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be looking at the fact that all upsets are spiritual in origin and common sources,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how to survive these inner trials, how to avoid disillusionment, despair, and self-hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,false teachers and how to spot them, the failure of discernment.
