Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The view of the world that must come out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The self-hatred that will come out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.52,0:29:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And the inner feeling of being destroyed by this teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.66,0:29:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to get into the study of such a pathway, then you will see what is going
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.58,0:29:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.96,0:29:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And at least you're going in with your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.27,0:29:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the teachings, as we said, of existentialism, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.57,0:29:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which teach...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.57,0:29:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which teach of man's hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.88,0:29:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have teachings then based on worshipping of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.98,0:30:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In which there is a great deal of grief and self-pity for what has befallen this group
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.24,0:30:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have teachings and teachers who are expressing and exploiting primarily this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.82,0:30:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,called fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.95,0:30:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case the person experiences then a fear of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.39,0:30:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is a punitive God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.60,0:30:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So these teachings are accompanied by fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.22,0:30:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that the energy field is in a negative direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It will engender fear and further fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.56,0:30:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see the exploitation of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.48,0:30:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these fields also have those who are adept at...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.00,0:30:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can sound convincing as they talk about the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.46,0:30:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They are almost like politicians in the religious or spiritual world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.34,0:30:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Very adept at...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.06,0:30:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At their convincingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet when we ask, you know, what is their energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.56,0:30:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the direction of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.20,0:31:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We find that the teaching of fear is negative and destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.22,0:31:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And we watch them on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.62,0:31:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We turn off the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.60,0:31:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We turn off the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.74,0:31:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And we look at the face and we see what the face is revealing when it's been disconnected
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.88,0:31:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,from the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.60,0:31:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we test it with kinesiology we'll see that people go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.94,0:31:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This indicating...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.10,0:31:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is being taught is not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.66,0:31:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem from our research that God is not at the bottom of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.14,0:31:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact all the teachings that come out of the bottom of the box all indicate the reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.90,0:31:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up into angriness then we will see those positions which promote anger, conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.18,0:31:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hatred and religious wars because they are competitive positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.12,0:31:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.12,0:31:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And God is usually championed then as a God of retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.24,0:32:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And because it's a polarized position of us being right and you being wrong, it's always
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,viewed that God will punish the non-believers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.40,0:32:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the punishment of the non-believers is usually one of the traditional teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.00,0:32:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we want to know this is we want to know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.84,0:32:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.78,0:32:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not saying that it's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.28,0:32:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do know where we are then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.28,0:32:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that we are in the energy fields of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.72,0:32:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We know we do know how it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.76,0:32:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We know we calibrate and how it correlates then with those things when which we can verify
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.38,0:32:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are truthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.46,0:32:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of all this then is to create a safe context, a safe orientation, a safe
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.18,0:32:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,space in which to do our spiritual work because in the spiritual work we're going to be committing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.10,0:32:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,our self to certain goals, certain purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.02,0:32:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.02,0:32:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be bringing up certain things in that process. And very often one cause of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.47,0:33:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual crises is that the person forgets that they have, through their own intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.81,0:33:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,initiated a process and that what they're experiencing now is a result of their having
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.73,0:33:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,asked the question, their having made the commitment, their having aligned themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.87,0:33:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with the search for the truth, their having defined themselves in a certain way and has
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.04,0:33:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,great power. And when we look at the power of mind, we see how powerful it is. It has
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.58,0:33:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then the power to bring up within your life the very thing you've asked for. So often
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.27,0:33:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of a crisis, what has happened is that the person has forgotten this, that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.11,0:33:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the person has really asked to bring up that which needs to be healed. And therefore, what
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.87,0:33:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is occurring in their life is not a mistake. It's not an error. It's exactly what needs
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.57,0:33:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to be brought up to be looked at, to be understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.65,0:34:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To be surrendered, to be re-contextualized, to be healed, to be forgiven. And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.05,0:34:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to come from a compassionate view. How can we heal that which comes up in our
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.15,0:34:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,life, if we ask for it to come up in our life, unless we're coming from a healing position?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.25,0:34:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, now you see how critically important it is to know what is the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.23,0:34:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,field of a given teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.82,0:34:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it requires forgiveness…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.64,0:34:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings of the Christ based on forgiveness, if it requires compassion and understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.24,0:34:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then the teaching will have to be in a positive direction, and it will certainly have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.00,0:34:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,500 and over, because we know that healing begins at 540. That which the world calls
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.64,0:34:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sin is obviously something that requires to be healed, is it not? So we'll need some teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.69,0:34:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then that is in a positive direction and is at least an energy field of 540. To ask
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.57,0:35:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,people to bring up from within themselves into a negative energy field is to bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.81,0:35:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what? The destruction. And therefore, it is unsafe to go into any spiritual teaching whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.63,0:35:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that suggests introspection and soul searching and purification, unless the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.20,0:35:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of that teaching itself is positive and at least to 540, that the teacher, the guru,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.88,0:35:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway, whatever. You can see how dangerous it would be. It would be like putting yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.36,0:35:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on the operating table and letting your abdomen be opened up by a surgeon who doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.20,0:35:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the skill to handle what he's going to discover when he gets there. So we don't allow a second-year
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.88,0:35:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,medical student to open up the abdomens on the operating table. We have to have someone
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.30,0:35:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who has the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.18,0:35:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So these energy fields are of power. It requires a great deal of power and knowledge to open
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.36,0:36:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,up one's insides and begin to investigate them. So we don't advise introspection and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.42,0:36:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of that inner process of purification until you know that the teacher and the teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.84,0:36:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and those around you are in this energy field of at least 540, which you see is nurturing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.86,0:36:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,supporting, forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.86,0:36:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's purpose is understanding and to heal through understanding and through compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.81,0:36:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The god of that kind of an energy field would therefore be a god who loves you because healing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.49,0:36:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,only comes about through loving and his love would be unconditional. If we understand the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.14,0:36:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,nature of God at all, we realize that that which is godly is unconditional. That which
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.60,0:36:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is conditional and is therefore limited by definition. It could have always been godly
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.56,0:36:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or unconditional. It could have always been godly or unconditional. There is a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.82,0:36:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it could hardly be godly. That which is God is beyond all conditions, infinite. So its
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.26,0:37:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,love is therefore infinite lovingness and therefore infinitely capable of a healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.92,0:37:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To create a safe context and a safe space for ourself then, it is necessary to know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.50,0:37:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are in a safe space, that the teacher and the teaching is positive in direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.04,0:37:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that its energy fuel is at least 540, that it holds compassion and forgiveness in a very
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.09,0:37:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,high place within the teaching, otherwise it will be unable to heal that which is brought
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.91,0:37:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.30,0:37:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The work that I did with my coworker, Glorian Ross, we checked out and calibrated literally
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.70,0:37:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thousands, in fact tens of thousands of factors in various teachings and various pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.92,0:37:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We found out
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.60,0:38:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,consistently that those which calibrated the highest and had the highest ratings and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.14,0:38:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,were in a positive direction were all characterized by the absence of teachings of hatred or condemnation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.04,0:38:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in any way. We found that what characterized the great teachers and the great teachings,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.02,0:38:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,those that calibrated at over 600 in a positive direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.88,0:38:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was a great compassion. Coming from an infinite compassion and forgivingness towards one's
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.46,0:38:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,humanness. Viewing it as something that needed to be healed. We saw a lack of concern with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.02,0:38:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a person's money or status. We saw that there was no desire to control the person's personal
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.78,0:38:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.12,0:38:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no make wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.44,0:38:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or invalidation of life in any of its aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.32,0:38:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And how is this so?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.96,0:39:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it isn't, for instance, money itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.34,0:39:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but the way that it's held,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.26,0:39:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,not the events of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.16,0:39:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but one's position about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.58,0:39:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the great teachings,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.06,0:39:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which are in a very positive direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.56,0:39:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,have to do with basic principles,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.50,0:39:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,have to do with principles
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.24,0:39:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,which one can experience the truth of within oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.70,0:39:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Through one's own inner spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.78,0:39:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The creation of a safe space, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.38,0:39:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of teachers who have no ways to exploit,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.94,0:39:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who have no ways to invalidate,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.96,0:39:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who are therefore themselves examples of their own principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.92,0:39:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exploitation of the followers for the sake of the movement or the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.42,0:39:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, there is the avoidance of that polarization
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.30,0:39:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of us and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.50,0:39:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a need for us against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.38,0:40:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a necessity to keep clear the difference between the phenomenal world,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.12,0:40:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the phenomenological phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.80,0:40:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So we notice that there is no preoccupation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.28,0:40:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with things in form in the unseen world,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.04,0:40:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually basic principles,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.36,0:40:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which then express through all the levels of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.96,0:40:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if we may use that term.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.56,0:40:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the great teachers have no interest in influencing your money
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.44,0:40:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or your life decisions, your personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.56,0:40:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of them actually refuse to answer questions on that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.28,0:40:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, what they exemplify and speak of is the teaching of a principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.72,0:40:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is then left up to the student or the follower
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.92,0:40:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern how to apply that principle in the given situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.64,0:40:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And so there are no make-wrongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.12,0:40:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no make-wrongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.96,0:40:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only the teaching of a greater context
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.68,0:41:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from which to hold that life experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.45,0:41:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we can get a better understanding of this
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.17,0:41:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,if we go back to the board
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.17,0:41:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at how these various things can be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.89,0:41:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We take an event in the world, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.29,0:41:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and the event in itself is of no particular significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.89,0:41:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how we hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.05,0:41:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the meaning that we project to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.37,0:41:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the significance that we give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.93,0:41:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself, it really has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.09,0:41:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So meaning is projected onto it by ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.49,0:41:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what that meaning will be will depend on our own level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.05,0:41:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness of the teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.41,0:41:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And so let us take money, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.13,0:41:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is such a source of conflict amongst spiritual seekers,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.85,0:41:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,at least in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.08,0:41:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How would money be looked at, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.92,0:41:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How would money be looked at, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.84,0:41:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,be looked at depending on the energy field of the teaching or the teacher. It could be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.82,0:42:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,something that you would feel guilty about. It would be something that it is sinful to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.84,0:42:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have and God will destroy you if you have money and you can hate yourself for having
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.28,0:42:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it and the whole process, of course, is a destructive one because it is a negative energy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,field with a very low calibration as far as truth. You might say that these numbers indicate
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.88,0:42:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the degree of truth, 600 and over being, moving into what is called absolute truth, the numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.50,0:42:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom having the least truth. We could then move up the energy field and we might
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.92,0:42:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,move into this of fear in which having money then would be a frightening thing, worry and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.36,0:42:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,anxiety and panic coming out of it. It would be viewed as unspiritual and as we said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.26,0:42:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God will punish you about this or it might be the source of hatred and resentment and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.48,0:42:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,grievance and the money then being used by the spiritual group in a competitive way,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.60,0:43:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,retaliatory towards others, leading to anger and religious war or money might be then held
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.30,0:43:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from pride in which it is status, so that your money would be a status symbol that God
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.40,0:43:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,has given you, you see. The more God loves you, the more money he gives you and this
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.04,0:43:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming from an inflated process. We might move up to a higher energy field and we
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.49,0:43:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we might say that the person here now becomes unattached to the money. He is released. It
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.27,0:43:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't run him anymore. It now becomes okay to have money because the God of that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.05,0:43:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,field you see is a God of freedom. Whether you have money or not is not something God
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.93,0:43:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is concerned about at all. As we move up, you might even be willing to now see this
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.25,0:43:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,differently and move into acceptance. As you move on up into the energy fields of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.64,0:43:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,gratitude is about 540. One might now view this money totally differently. One might
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.97,0:44:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,view it as a gift from God about which one is grateful, that the money would then be
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.01,0:44:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a way, a tool, a way of expressing your compassion and your unconditional lovingness towards
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.01,0:44:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the suffering of the world because the energy field of love nurtures and supports love,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.75,0:44:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,life in all of its reflections.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.15,0:44:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.71,0:44:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.81,0:44:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.83,0:44:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.85,0:44:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Revelation, because there is the release, as we said, in the brain of endorphins, the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.37,0:44:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing of it as loving then, it might be seen then as a loving thing, that money is a way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.81,0:44:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,now to support others. And therefore you see the intention behind it, the way that it is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.65,0:44:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,held would now view this money as a blessing, as a responsibility, as a way of helping others,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.01,0:44:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of supporting others. So the money then would be used for the benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.03,0:44:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind, not as an egotistical gesture where you get your name on a brass plate that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.69,0:45:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so and so gave this to that organization. But to use that then as a gift, acknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.25,0:45:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the source, to acknowledge the source as the love of God and to view it as an expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.23,0:45:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, as you move towards the top of the field into oneness and perfection, you see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.23,0:45:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,all things are aspects of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.25,0:45:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God being all that is, you begin to see the divinity within all things. And this would
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.64,0:45:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then apply to everything in your life. So money, instead of being sinful now, would
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.34,0:45:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,be a tool that God has given you so that you can express your lovingness in a greater field
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.14,0:45:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and help large numbers of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.53,0:45:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It could then be held from joy in which one would feel an inner gladness that one has
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.31,0:45:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.59,0:46:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the power, money here being an expression of God's power on earth to bring about the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.23,0:46:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,healing of the inner pain and suffering of mankind. The expression and nurturing of love
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.65,0:46:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then is the desire, coming out of compassion, for the relief of suffering. And so the money
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.17,0:46:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,would then become a tool in which you could help relieve the suffering of the world and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.85,0:46:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.43,0:46:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the great beings have done that. Whatever assets they had were held as gifts from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.11,0:46:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the gift was then utilized to bring about the increasing knowledge of man and the relief
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.18,0:46:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of suffering that comes about through the progressive increase of man's knowledge of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.18,0:46:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.70,0:46:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one is always sex, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.98,0:46:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's take a look at sex and how sex and the conflicts arising around that are held
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.18,0:46:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,depending upon the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.78,0:47:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see that sex, an event in human life, part of humanness, can be held from the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.64,0:47:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.24,0:47:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field, the teaching coming out of this energy field, would then view it as
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.22,0:47:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,negative as associated with sin and suffering for which God, the God of that level, is the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.14,0:47:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,great destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.18,0:47:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole process is one of destruction and self-hatred, self-pity, self-blame, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.14,0:47:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one would be that sex and the conflicts arising around that are held depending upon
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.08,0:47:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field, regardless of what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.32,0:47:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hopeless condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.42,0:47:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Man's sexuality is hopeless and his whole condition is one of despair and loss of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.45,0:47:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do we mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.01,0:47:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We mean aliveness, the capacity to experience the aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.98,0:47:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we might view it as sad and regretful that man is an animal, let's say, that which
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.30,0:47:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,views it, views man as a body because at the bottom here we're viewing man, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.34,0:47:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.34,0:47:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Subsequently, the body as a contact with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.34,0:47:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Subsequently, the body as an link with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.44,0:47:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Subsequently, the body as an link with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.56,0:48:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the line of the truth he is less and less viewed as a body and progressively realizes that he is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.08,0:48:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,spirit but that which views man his body then would condemn it how sad it is that man is such
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.46,0:48:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,an animal those who are coming out of fear would view sexuality then with worry anxiety and panic
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.70,0:48:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole subject is frightening best to deny and just ignore it altogether because the god of that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.10,0:48:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,level is punitive and would punish you for any sexuality we can move on up now you can see the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.64,0:48:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,various ways the angriness with which it can be held the people people who hate themselves for
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.68,0:48:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,their own sexuality etc and then those who exploit seduction etc the perversions of religion the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.84,0:48:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,occult demon what do we call them satanic societies etc in which the sexuality and the seduction
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.14,0:48:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,now is reversed and it's
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.42,0:48:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,expression then becomes an inflated one in which its importance is inflated out of proportion
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.87,0:49:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how would sexuality then be held once we get up to the level of truth these are all negative energy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.87,0:49:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,fields from the level of truth to begin to face and cope and handle what is sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.71,0:49:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know in from the whole viewpoint of spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.23,0:49:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to become empowered now to take the opportunity because the god here is one of an open mind
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.15,0:49:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of freedom the freedom it's okay to explore this because this says here we're not
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.91,0:49:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,attached to any position about it what we're coming from now is the humility you see this
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.20,0:49:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is the beginning of humility meaning i really don't know the answer to this one i really don't
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.88,0:49:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and i'm willing however to begin to look at it now the willingness because it's a positive energy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.76,0:49:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,field says this is a friendly promising and hopeful subject we can look into
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.22,0:49:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,um we've added our own intention now to clear up the subject and we start feeling a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.18,0:50:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,confidence that we have the capacity in a harmonious world with a merciful god now to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.94,0:50:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,explore it without being thrown into hellfire we move on up into an energy field of 500 and over
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.29,0:50:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's held from the viewpoint of lovingness and gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.80,0:50:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it is seen now as an expression of nurturance nurturance and support and healingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.64,0:50:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,making love in itself is a healing forgiving act people who have argued and fought etc in the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.92,0:50:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,embrace forgive each other nurture and heal each other re reaffirm each other's worth and value
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.64,0:50:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and so now sexuality becomes an expression of love it eventually becomes an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.76,0:50:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of unconditional love it becomes an expression of the joy and the celebration of one's own alive and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.40,0:50:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,existence a gratitude to god for the joy of existence the beginning of transfiguration and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.84,0:51:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,revelation the moving on to bliss and those who then move on to high states of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.80,0:51:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,see it as an expression of oneness an expression of oneness a way of being
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.69,0:51:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a way of being and a way of joining those two great energies the masculine and the feminine in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.93,0:51:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.05,0:51:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you see sexuality then, or money, any of these things, the view about them now is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.57,0:51:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,only a view, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.02,0:51:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In none of these instances can we say what is the thing in and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.96,0:51:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot take it out of the field of understanding which is coming out of this level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.56,0:51:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So when a person or a teaching expresses their attitudes, their beliefs, their opinions,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.08,0:51:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,many of these things we will find out are merely opinions about a thing, they are not
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.54,0:52:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about the thing itself, they are talking about how they hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.90,0:52:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And how they hold it then is an expression of their level of consciousness, their degree
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.26,0:52:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of awareness of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.32,0:52:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The lower their view, the more negative they will look at any human behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.11,0:52:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And all things can be held from a make-wrong, because the bottom of the box is an endless
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.33,0:52:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,make-wrong, the invalidation of life in all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.73,0:52:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that work can be viewed as a make-wrong, all man's intentions, all man's impulses,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.87,0:52:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,his biology, his psychology, even his spiritual ambitions, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.23,0:52:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your desire to be a spiritual seeker can be invalidated, because there is sure
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.53,0:52:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to be somebody that says, well, you are just coming from a spiritual ego, you are just
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.91,0:52:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.91,0:52:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you just want to realize the truth for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.15,0:52:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so even your spiritual work itself can become invalidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.41,0:53:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And so these are ways of using the truth against the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.25,0:53:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we move out of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.69,0:53:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can move out of it by seeing clearly what we just said, that there is the event in the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.23,0:53:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,world, there is life itself, there is human nature, and that is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.39,0:53:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.09,0:53:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a way of being with that, a way of viewing it, how you hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.59,0:53:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is expressing a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.83,0:53:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still not saying anything about that out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.43,0:53:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we find is being talked about is one's own level of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.51,0:53:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing really being said about the world, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.13,0:53:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because those who are at the very top, the enlightened beings, all say that all is God,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.22,0:53:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that a thing is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.64,0:53:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That all is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.64,0:53:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They place no construction on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.53,0:53:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They give no valuation of right or wrong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.03,0:54:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the sacredness of all of existence, and therefore there is no invalidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.15,0:54:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If all is God, then to invalidate any part of it would be invalidating God.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.21,0:54:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Man being God's creation, the least of all to invalidate man and his various expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.62,0:54:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, what is taught is a principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.12,0:54:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the principle would lead you to understand that coming out of this just doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.18,0:54:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you find the highest teachers will tell you that if you follow this course, such and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.54,0:54:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,such will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.06,0:54:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And they leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.36,0:54:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a very good example in our society of such pure teaching is that of Alcoholics
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.65,0:54:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anonymous, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.65,0:54:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes no position about whether you drink or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.55,0:54:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't try to close up the liquor industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.31,0:54:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't try to convince you that you should stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.45,0:54:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But it says, for those who had a problem, this is what we did, and these were the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.69,0:54:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you continue on drinking, these will be the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.61,0:54:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no make wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.71,0:55:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no invalidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.69,0:55:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not looking for any power.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.25,0:55:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not looking to exploit anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.43,0:55:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.09,0:55:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.73,0:55:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no government.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.73,0:55:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.86,0:55:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no glamour.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.82,0:55:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just pure spiritual principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.46,0:55:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that allows...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.44,0:55:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It allows the individual to have the freedom to see the truth in that for himself and if
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.94,0:55:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he wishes to apply it to his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.82,0:55:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see exemplified there that which is a high teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.60,0:55:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And that particular organization, when we calibrate it, does come out at 540, as we
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.86,0:55:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,would expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.86,0:55:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,An energy field which heals would have to be a teaching that is in a positive direction
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.66,0:55:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and it calibrates out at least 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.51,0:55:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And they stand, of course, as an example of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.23,0:55:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The healing there is based on the physical, the mental and the spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.37,0:55:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's said that no healing from addiction occurs without spiritual growth and development.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.83,0:56:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened in the lives of many people that are considered saints and wrote autobiographies,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.99,0:56:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,etc., in which this bottom of the box played a big part in their inner experience prior
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.89,0:56:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to their achieving a higher state of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.42,0:56:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened was the progressive influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.46,0:56:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.46,0:56:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The progressive influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.46,0:56:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As they moved, you see, in their research into their inner selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.88,0:56:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally moved and brought up the very bottom of the box and faced the unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.00,0:56:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and now conscious conception of self as that which is ultimately separated from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.90,0:56:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of the box is the ultimate separation from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.64,0:56:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Until finally the agony, the self-hatred of the exquisite sense of sinfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.62,0:56:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then brought about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.32,0:56:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brought about not the discovery of God within sin,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.10,0:56:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but it brought about surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.47,0:57:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened in each and every case was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.73,0:57:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the agonizing experience of being so far from God
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.71,0:57:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was so agonizing that the person let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.13,0:57:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the willingness to let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.07,0:57:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to accept God as God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.78,0:57:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened then is they moved up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.46,0:57:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to a situation called surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.66,0:57:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender, when we calibrate the energy field of surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.98,0:57:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it is 575.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.40,0:57:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened is the person removed themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.24,0:57:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,from a minus 30 energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.66,0:57:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally gave up and surrendered to God
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.56,0:57:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,an energy field of 575
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.91,0:57:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and opened the way to the experience of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.61,0:57:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so those who became enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.07,0:57:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,often went through,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.81,0:57:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,agonizing periods,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.13,0:57:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,agonizing periods,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.35,0:57:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,40 days of facing that which is the utmost negative
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.59,0:58:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,buried within one's unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.71,0:58:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,owning one's own shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.83,0:58:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at that which the person has held as most hateful
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.17,0:58:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and owning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.75,0:58:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But the enlightenment then came about
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.53,0:58:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,through first the owning of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.31,0:58:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but then it was the letting go of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.61,0:58:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The letting go of that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.03,0:58:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the farthest,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.51,0:58:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the most removed from the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.39,0:58:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in those positions that are coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.97,0:58:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the bottom of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.11,0:58:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was the letting go of those positions
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.29,0:58:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that come out of the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.55,0:58:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that led to the realization of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.49,0:58:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which brings us to then what is the overall
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.61,0:58:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,general nature of spiritual work itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.01,0:58:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the progressive letting go of positions
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.57,0:58:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and moving into an ever enlarging context.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.21,0:58:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We could say,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.96,0:58:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that all that is within the box is the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.12,0:58:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All that is within the box is the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.56,0:59:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,High ego states,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.44,0:59:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,lower ego states.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.78,0:59:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The letting go progressively,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.58,0:59:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,because these are all representing points of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.54,0:59:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The progressive letting go of points of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.68,0:59:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the letting go of judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.82,0:59:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the letting go of the vanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.84,0:59:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the vanity coming out of here of I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.92,0:59:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.92,0:59:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The coming to the surrender through humility here
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.56,0:59:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of allowing the process of revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.52,0:59:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.60,0:59:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's that the truth becomes revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.74,0:59:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see the progressive letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.64,0:59:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of these restrictive positions,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.30,0:59:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,all of which block the inner consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.82,0:59:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and awareness of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.77,0:59:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness of the truth then is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.21,0:59:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically of an energy field which gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.23,0:59:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,progressively higher until finally it reaches a point
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.63,1:00:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,where one is open to the grace of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.66,1:00:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That brings us to another difficulty in spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.12,1:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which brings about crises and conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.94,1:00:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the use of the term ego
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.50,1:00:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in a pejorative, make wrong kind of a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.90,1:00:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, people will say,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.72,1:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that is only ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.32,1:00:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your whole life has just been ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.86,1:00:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your whole life is a nurse or a doctor
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.84,1:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,or a spiritual teacher or a mechanic,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.01,1:00:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you happen to be doing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.85,1:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an ego trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.48,1:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As we look at this, we'll see from the viewpoint of truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.96,1:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing as just ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.92,1:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It would mean that there is some place where God is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.52,1:00:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, all things represent,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.12,1:00:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,let us say all positions represent ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.16,1:00:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but the ego then is superimposed on that which is not ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.16,1:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be something larger, consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.16,1:01:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so to safely do spiritual work and avoid crises,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.16,1:01:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's necessary to reaffirm and look within
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.16,1:01:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and discover one's own innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.16,1:01:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is really not safe to do spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.16,1:01:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,unless one has a glimpse at that innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.16,1:01:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and keeps one eye on it at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.16,1:01:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that innocence then is the gateway back to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.16,1:01:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so that one doesn't get lost in the swirling of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.38,1:01:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what we're going to talk about today.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.12,1:01:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to talk about the spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.06,1:01:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to talk about the spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.20,1:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to talk about how the child is re-discovered
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.00,1:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it's re-recognized in the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.00,1:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do we see that innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.00,1:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and how can we know its presence?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.00,1:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that enlightened beings say that all are one with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.00,1:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, that which is intrinsically innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.92,1:01:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is within us at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.92,1:01:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In our other talks, we have talked about how to rediscover that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.92,1:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've said that it can come about as a matter of revelation
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.92,1:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or it can come about as a matter of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.10,1:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If we look at the consciousness of the child,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.08,1:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And all, everyone agrees on the innocence of the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.94,1:02:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His little consciousness is yet, is not devious.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.88,1:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't learned to lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.14,1:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't learned the value of, the spurious values of judgment and criticism.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.79,1:02:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So the child is openly trusting and innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.89,1:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of his innocence and his trustiness is where he begins to learn that which is not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.21,1:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He hears his parents say, we don't play with certain children because they're of the wrong race or creed or color.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.01,1:02:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They belong to the wrong religion.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.41,1:02:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And so hatred is taught to the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.23,1:02:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We, in other words, to be loyal to our family and if you honor and love your mother and your father,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.11,1:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the child then has to adopt that teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.65,1:02:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the innocence of the child then is exploited by that which is not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.95,1:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which is not the truth comes through generation after generation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.21,1:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocently enough through the parents, and through the grandparents, and through the family members,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.09,1:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and through friends and relatives, and through the teachers, and through television, and the storybooks, and the novels.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.38,1:03:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that which is intrinsically innocent begins to take on to itself programs, beliefs, which are not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.16,1:03:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You might compare the consciousness of the child to the hardware of a computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.46,1:03:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the programming coming in from social consciousness from the world itself as the software.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.58,1:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.62,1:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that in the computer, the hardware, that which is intrinsically innocent, is uncontaminated by the software.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.02,1:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run any kind of ignorance or negativity or falsehood through a computer, and the computer itself is uncontaminated.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.86,1:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You put on the next soft floppy disk, and the computer's capacity is unimpaired.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.14,1:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that intrinsic innocence within consciousness itself is unimpaired.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.18,1:03:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we've said in other talks, it is that intrinsic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.62,1:03:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocence that is listening to this voice speaking right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.30,1:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the intrinsic innocence of one's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.50,1:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening, trying to find the truth, trying to attune itself to what is real in this, what is...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.38,1:04:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That childlike innocence is unchanged throughout our entire life.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.66,1:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It never leaves us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.34,1:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And so when we look at what the world calls ego, or what spiritual work calls ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.90,1:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of condemning it, we just see that out of innocence, that's what we believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.62,1:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we believed at that time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.62,1:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What we did was appropriate, if that software program was correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.93,1:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, we don't ever make a mistake in our spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.49,1:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.65,1:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we set our intention in achieving an understanding of the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.68,1:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in being open to grace so that the truth may be revealed,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.52,1:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,however you wish to hold it in your own mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.04,1:04:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,whichever expression is most appropriate for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.30,1:05:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you must remember that you have asked all that is in error to be brought up for recognition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.74,1:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right to do that if you realize at the same time your innate innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.02,1:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The innocence of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.78,1:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The innocence not of you as a person, the innocence of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.58,1:05:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you as a person are merely reflecting that which is universal,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.74,1:05:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.50,1:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And what has gone on then has gone on as a result of the nature of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.78,1:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore there's no point in going into personal self-condemnation about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.26,1:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nor is there, on the opposite side of the coin, going into personal pride about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.90,1:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The discovery of the nature of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.58,1:05:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,looking into the nature of that consciousness through your own introspection,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.50,1:05:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you will realize that everything you've ever believed in your whole life,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.46,1:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you believed it out of your own innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.54,1:05:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see that, you then develop a compassion and understanding,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.18,1:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.70,1:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your compassion now,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.38,1:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your compassion,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.58,1:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,how through their own innocence,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.06,1:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody has come to believe what they believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.98,1:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness then to forgive allows you to see into the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.10,1:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see into the hearts of others,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.74,1:06:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your own compassion,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.26,1:06:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you see over and over again the innocence of the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.74,1:06:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the age of the body,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.66,1:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness has remained unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.70,1:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You still hear the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.54,1:06:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the heart of the child within the adult, saying, but won't we all, but don't we, and it's the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.93,1:06:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,innocence of the child still speaking. To keep an eye on that and prevent spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.81,1:06:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,crises, it heals them as they come up. The reaffirmation of our innocence, then, never
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.04,1:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,buying that anything is just ego. There is no such thing as just ego. Ego, the software,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.75,1:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,social consciousness, the programming has been superimposed on that which is not ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.51,1:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is truth itself, consciousness itself. All spiritual crisis, then, comes
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.77,1:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,out of context. It comes out of meaning. It comes out of the way in which a thing is held.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.83,1:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think your diet, for instance, is an unspiritual diet, or your lifestyle is an
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.88,1:07:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,unspiritual lifestyle, or what you do for a living, all of these things are merely reflecting,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.16,1:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as we see now, a certain level of consciousness. Those who have reached very high levels of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.76,1:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.98,1:07:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Condemn nothing. They will affirm, however, that certain levels of consciousness will
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.09,1:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,have consequences. That a certain lifestyle, a lifestyle of selling out, selling out the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.60,1:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,truth about yourself, will bring inner pain and grievance. And now it's left up to you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.90,1:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you wish to continue to do so or not. But there is no attempt to control you, no
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.72,1:07:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,attempt to control you. Even the use of hell there, the thought of hell, and the hells are
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.44,1:08:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,down below here. They are reversed fields. They are not only 30, 50, 75. They are like
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.12,1:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a minus 30, minus 50, minus 75, down to minus 100. Even those are then held as merely the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.64,1:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,consequences that will come about from certain types of behavior. Not as a threat, not something
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.78,1:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to frighten or control people with, not holding that as a negative position, but merely saying
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.44,1:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that certain behavior is not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.70,1:08:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That certain behavior, certain kinds of self condemnation, etc., will bring you into energy
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.88,1:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,fields that you will experience as the hells. Then it's left up to you whether you wish
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.26,1:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue to do that or not. But hell is not then a threat. It would merely be a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.94,1:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of human consciousness. A fact of human consciousness. That the inner agony can become greater than
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.00,1:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is already if you violate certain principles.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.48,1:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the teaching still holds up then that it can be a very high teaching even though
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.68,1:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it may warn us that very agonizing and painful states of consciousness can come about as
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.16,1:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a result of certain behavior.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.72,1:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All experience within human consciousness, that includes of course all of spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.08,1:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is representing a position. It's representing a way of being with, a way of holding. And
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.60,1:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're always talking about then, even though when we think we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.72,1:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the external world, is really an inner position coming out of a certain level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.04,1:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How we are with a thing, how we can choose to be with it. And the pains and the agonies
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.86,1:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that come about are coming about as a result of our hanging on to, hanging on to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.12,1:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging on to putting our survival on something that is not the truth. Pain tells us that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.55,1:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we have,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.73,1:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've been hanging on to something, that we've put our survival on to something which
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.37,1:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is a violation of some principle of consciousness. And that really is what spiritual work is about.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.63,1:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So the progressive pain then of these positions is telling us that they are far from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.07,1:10:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that they're wrong. You see, there's no make wrong. It's that as you get closer
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.53,1:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and closer to the experience of the presence of God, the inner experience is one of increasing
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.73,1:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,joy and happiness. As we get farther from it, it tells us that we are far removed from
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.17,1:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth. Therefore, it's not a make wrong. It's not right or wrong. It's just that it's
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.59,1:10:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,painful and doesn't work. Coming out of desiringness, for instance, the Buddha said that all pain
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.73,1:10:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffering is based on desiringness. And a greater elaboration of that is that the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.91,1:10:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,desiringness is coming out of a fear, and the fear is coming out of a sense of lack,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.83,1:10:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.73,1:11:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,belief that one is separated from God. So he's not saying that you can't desire anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.42,1:11:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just saying that desiringness itself is going to lead to progressive frustration
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.18,1:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and a feeling of being separated from the truth, and that you're going to be constantly
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.36,1:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting and craving, and that you're going to be entrapped by that. There's no right
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.17,1:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or wrong about it. There's no saying we should go to war with those people. Those people
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.39,1:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have souls, and God hates them and will throw them into hell. No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.53,1:11:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All he's saying is that the consequences of this endless frustration is going to lead
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.53,1:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to anger. If you acquire that which you desire, you're going to go into pridefulness. If you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.47,1:11:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,don't, you're going to fear that you're going to lose it. If you keep trying and don't make
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.23,1:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it, you're going to go into apathy and guilt. So all he's saying is that the consequences
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.37,1:11:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,are negative. The consequences are not going to support your movement towards the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.78,1:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we notice that in these energy fields that one negative level of energy tends to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.50,1:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,bring forth all of them. So that desiringness doesn't remain pure, it tends to bring with
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.02,1:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it anger and pride and fear and grief and apathy. And so grief tends to pull with it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.08,1:12:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,fearful, angry, desiringness. And each of these tends to pull the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.56,1:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The critical point in all spiritual work then is this capacity to be willing to tell the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.78,1:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,truth. Very often that truth is, I don't know. And it's the out of I don't know comes the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.96,1:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,willingness to be willing to tell the truth. And it's the out of I don't know comes the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.50,1:12:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,willingness to surrender, which is 575, to God. And the truth then comes about through
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.16,1:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,an act of surrender. The truth then out of the pain, which leads many people into spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.66,1:12:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,work, is not coming out of the pain. And the mistake is to worship the pain and think that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.00,1:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering therefore is the royal road to enlightenment. It's the realization by facing all the suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.92,1:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,within oneself that it is not the truth. And it is the willingness to let it go and surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.70,1:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it to God that the truth is revealed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.67,1:13:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our whole position then about our inner innocence, the remembering that when we start spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.63,1:13:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,work we are asking to have that which is not the truth brought up to our awareness and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.67,1:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore it is evidence of success. Therefore the somewhat chaotic appearance of the lives
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.80,1:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of people who are labeled spiritual seekers, many of them their life becomes somewhat chaotic
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.56,1:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to the outside observer.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.40,1:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner person is pleased because it says, I've asked to see what stands between me and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.72,1:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth and that has been brought up for my awareness to be recognized, re-owned, re-contextualized
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.40,1:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and healed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.47,1:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How to come from a safe context then about one's spiritual work? How to provide for yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.89,1:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a safe space? To come from the heart, that which is the heart with a capital H, not the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.81,1:14:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,physical heart, but the ultimate compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.43,1:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The owning of oneself from this level, the joy of the spiritual work, the saying thank
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.03,1:14:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you to all the things that come up out of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.43,1:14:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The crisis is the very event of the spiritual healing. It is out of the crisis that the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.55,1:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,healing occurs.
